1.Open Git Bash:

  bash here
  
2.Clone your fork:

  git clone https://github.com/kangris-sket/appinventor-sources.git

3.Add remote from original repository in your forked repository:

  cd appinventor-sources
  git remote add upstream https://github.com/mit-cml/appinventor-sources.git
  cp sample-.gitignore .gitignore
  git submodule update --init
  git fetch upstream
  git checkout master
  
4.Updating your fork from original repo to keep up with their changes:

  git pull upstream master
          or
  git merge upstream/master
